<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>أخرجه هناد في "الزهد<span class="c1">" <span class="c2">(٩٤٧)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
